input: Can you tell me how many prenote entries were turned down because there weren't enough funds in the bank account with the UUID 01234567-89ab-cdef-0123-456789abcdef?

output.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM BankAccountPrenoteEntry WHERE BankAccountUUID = '01234567-89ab-cdef-0123-456789abcdef' AND RejectionReasonName = 'Insufficient Funds';
